data.description: A spacious 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath brick front home situated on a generous 2.6 acre lot with a serene and beautiful pond. Embrace the beauty of nature while enjoying the ample living space this property offers. As you step inside, you will be greeted with a spacious living area filled with natural light that showcases the amazing hardwood floors. The family focal point, the kitchen, boosts ample counter space and a huge convenient breakfast bar.  The main level hosts the master suite and 2 secondary rooms with a shared bathroom. Upstairs is a full bedroom with private bath and an oversized room with a loft feel. Compliant with fair housing laws, this welcoming residence is ready to become your ideal home.
